data.description: This well-constructed home is nestled in the middle of Lafayette and is waiting for new owners to make it their own.  This traditional home welcomes visitors through a beveled glass front door and leads you into a formal foyer and oversized formal dining room.  The kitchen and living area share a space with a small breakfast space.  Out the back door, you can access a covered patio with a view to a half-acre lot. A clean 30'x30' shop on a slab with power sits in the backyard and is ready to customize.  Roof replaced in 2020. A/C replaced in 2019 and includes a 10-yr warranty.  Hot water tank replaced in 2020. Appliances may remain upon request.  Flood zone X.
